n class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> (Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ариза берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ариза берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000; font-weight: bold;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза тузилган жой </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза тузилган сана </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> турмуш ўртоғим </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза берувчининг турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> номига </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Бекор қилиниши сўралаётган олди-сотди шартномасини тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нотариал идораси нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Бекор қилиниши сўралаётган олди-сотди шартномасини тасдиқлаган нотариал идора нотариус Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Бекор қилиниши сўралаётган олди-сотди шартномаси тузилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Бекор қилиниши сўралаётган олди-сотди шартномасининг рўйхат рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-сонли реестр рақами билан расмийлаштирилган, </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Автотранспорт русуми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Автотранспорт воситаси ишлаб чиқарилган йил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да ишлаб чиқарилган, давлат рақами белгиси </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Автотранспорт воситасининг давлат рақам белгиси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бўлган автотранспорт воситасининг олди-сотди шартномасини бекор қилишига ўз розилигимни бераман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Келгусида мазкур автотранспорт воситаси бўйича бир-биримизга нисбатан ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмаймиз.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 48.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Оила кодексининг 23-24-моддалари мазмуни менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#9}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______________</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\">